roadhurst\"}, {\"begin\": 318, \"end\": 331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997855477372563, \"rank\": 0.00021449804351999748, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Broadhurst's hopes of qualifying for the 2024 Games for Ireland were dealt a huge blow this month when the Irish Athletic Boxing Association [IABA] told her she would not be going to the final Olympic qualifying tournament.\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 368, \"end\": 378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\", \"score\": 0.9999999771896457, \"rank\": 2.2810461230801948e-08, \"text\": \"Broadhurst\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q24354\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\"}, {\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9925463924927368, \"rank\": 0.006606175221136639, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Athletic_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Irish Athletic Boxing Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Athletic_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Athletic_Boxing_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old won gold in the light-welterweight division at the 2022 World Championships.That division (63kg) is not an Olympic weight, although Broadhurst has fought at lightweight (60kg) and won gold at the 2022 Commonwealth Games in that category.Amy Broadhurst wants to represent Great Britain at the Olympics|GETTYBroadhurst's problem is that Ireland's Kellie Harrington has already secured qualification for the lightweight category as the reigning Olympic champion in that weight.She also failed in her bid to qualify for the Olympics through last year's European Games when she lost to Great Britain's Rosie Eccles in the quarter-finals.Countries are only allowed to qualify one boxer per weight for the Paris Games and Great Britain do not yet have someone qualified for the 60kg category.The IABA have now revealed that Broadhurst has put in a request to switch allegiance to Great Britain in order to have a chance of qualifying for the Olympics.The statement reads: \\\"We were contacted by GB Boxing on behalf of Amy Broadhurst, who had indicated that she intends to seek a change of nationality in a bid to qualify for the Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 741, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\", \"score\": 0.9999999771896457, \"rank\": 2.2810461230801948e-08, \"text\": \"Broadhurst\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q24354\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\"}, {\"begin\": 850, \"end\": 860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\", \"score\": 0.9999999771896457, \"rank\": 2.2810461230801948e-08, \"text\": \"Broadhurst\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q24354\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\"}, {\"begin\": 880, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997855477372563, \"rank\": 0.00021449804351999748, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_O