ifying tournament in Bangkok.\", \"from\": 5427, \"to\": 5566, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5427, \"end\": 5437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\", \"score\": 0.9999999771896457, \"rank\": 2.2810461230801948e-08, \"text\": \"Broadhurst\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q24354\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Broadhurst_Theatre\"}, {\"begin\": 5460, \"end\": 5464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Athletic_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IABA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Athletic_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_Athletic_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 5558, \"end\": 5565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"score\": 0.9754929778432572, \"rank\": 0.021955668780095177, \"text\": \"Bangkok\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a bit of a mess and I am struggling to wrap my head around what is going on,\\\" she told BBC Sport NI.\", \"from\": 5568, \"to\": 5674, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5661, \"end\": 5670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999998672276521, \"rank\": 1.0580513494164852e-07, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LATEST SPORT NEWS:  Amy Broadhurst (right) with Katie Taylor at the undisputed super lightweight championship fight  GETTY  \\\"I have let my psychologist know to let them know that I will not be up in the high performance centre for the foreseeable future, and I will be really thinking about not going back up at all.\\\"\", \"from\": 5676, \"to\": 5993, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 572